{"tid":2053924,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想養熊仔鼠","createTime":"2020-06-06T16:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T10:13:32.000Z","uid":10566,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"693a69afe3075343e68f68d5b74de0d6bdcdcc62","tid":2053924,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"想買哂鼠鼠要用嘅嘢先揾鼠<br />\n但網上啲資料睇完都唔太明<br />\n所以上嚟問問<br />\n<br />\n倉鼠籠<br />\n已知要60x40x40大細<br />\n唔知只可以有一層或兩層都可以<br />\n有咩籠建議<br />\n<br />\nBedding<br />\n有上網揾但唔知有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糧食<br />\n只知道每日餵佢10分1體重嘅糧食<br />\n最好每日餵以免佢挑食<br />\n唔知纖維糧同營養糧嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n知道要有20cm以上輪盤<br />\n廁所<br />\n食物盤<br />\n水樽<br />\n大理石<br />\n<br />\n其他就唔太清楚 希望有人可以解答吓我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b508c0f7d564625ad055fa3cdd435c2c6db53c51","tid":2053924,"uid":217098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"693a69afe3075343e68f68d5b74de0d6bdcdcc62","tid":2053924,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"想買哂鼠鼠要用嘅嘢先揾鼠<br />\n但網上啲資料睇完都唔太明<br />\n所以上嚟問問<br />\n<br />\n倉鼠籠<br />\n已知要60x40x40大細<br />\n唔知只可以有一層或兩層都可以<br />\n有咩籠建議<br />\n<br />\nBedding<br />\n有上網揾但唔知有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糧食<br />\n只知道每日餵佢10分1體重嘅糧食<br />\n最好每日餵以免佢挑食<br />\n唔知纖維糧同營養糧嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n知道要有20cm以上輪盤<br />\n廁所<br />\n食物盤<br />\n水樽<br />\n大理石<br />\n<br />\n其他就唔太清楚 希望有人可以解答吓我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"細個養個時，買個大魚缸，再買輪盤<br />\n食既就掟曬入去，反正佢地都會草埋係個竇到<br />\n養左成年，大隻到手掌咁"},{"pid":"7db370ebed05ecba0c919b78799582baece0924a","tid":2053924,"uid":79817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"佢啲尿好似公廁咁臭"},{"pid":"30d476462a1bf59b1f19b4bdc3a5425841b3a307","tid":2053924,"uid":10544,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"唔好養啦 太短命喇"},{"pid":"342cadb90c0357636cdaeb956e730291ad45cf63","tid":2053924,"uid":83858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"693a69afe3075343e68f68d5b74de0d6bdcdcc62","tid":2053924,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"想買哂鼠鼠要用嘅嘢先揾鼠<br />\n但網上啲資料睇完都唔太明<br />\n所以上嚟問問<br />\n<br />\n倉鼠籠<br />\n已知要60x40x40大細<br />\n唔知只可以有一層或兩層都可以<br />\n有咩籠建議<br />\n<br />\nBedding<br />\n有上網揾但唔知有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糧食<br />\n只知道每日餵佢10分1體重嘅糧食<br />\n最好每日餵以免佢挑食<br />\n唔知纖維糧同營養糧嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n知道要有20cm以上輪盤<br />\n廁所<br />\n食物盤<br />\n水樽<br />\n大理石<br />\n<br />\n其他就唔太清楚 希望有人可以解答吓我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T17:35:13.000Z","msg":"籠：多數建議訂造整理箱或者sanko 60，但後者通風唔太好所以要睇返你養嘅環境而定。<br />\n<br />\nBedding：一係用廚紙，一係用紙棉。依家夏天薄薄鋪一層就ok，但冬天就要比多啲廚紙比佢地整。<br />\n<br />\n糧食：纖維糧同營養糧嘅分別在於前者佢地食完會令到便便容易成形同靚啲，而後者係比佢哋吸收返佢地需要嘅營養。基本配法：oxbow草圈+bunny糧+M糧（M糧只需1/2粒）如想佢地再多啲營養就可以隔數日比一次Harrison糊。記得唔好比瓜子！！就算比都一星期比1-2粒only<br />\n<br />\n其他：夏天可因應你既環境決定開冷氣/開風扇比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋佢地唔可以係太濕嘅環境！必要時開抽濕機！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7caf8cf3d40586f20178b60e6ffe39cb9565099e","tid":2053924,"uid":83858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"342cadb90c0357636cdaeb956e730291ad45cf63","tid":2053924,"uid":83858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"693a69afe3075343e68f68d5b74de0d6bdcdcc62","tid":2053924,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"想買哂鼠鼠要用嘅嘢先揾鼠<br />\n但網上啲資料睇完都唔太明<br />\n所以上嚟問問<br />\n<br />\n倉鼠籠<br />\n已知要60x40x40大細<br />\n唔知只可以有一層或兩層都可以<br />\n有咩籠建議<br />\n<br />\nBedding<br />\n有上網揾但唔知有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n糧食<br />\n只知道每日餵佢10分1體重嘅糧食<br />\n最好每日餵以免佢挑食<br />\n唔知纖維糧同營養糧嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n知道要有20cm以上輪盤<br />\n廁所<br />\n食物盤<br />\n水樽<br />\n大理石<br />\n<br />\n其他就唔太清楚 希望有人可以解答吓我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\